Author: mole99
Content:
Great work!

I just had a look at the layout in https://github.com/ishi-kai/ISHI-KAI_Multiple_Projects_WaferSapce-GF180-1/blob/main/gds/ISHI-KAI_WS_RUN1.zip and I noticed that the core area does not contain any filler cells. Does your design comply with the density rules?

I also saw that you moved the QR code from the bottom left corner to the top left corner. While this is fine, is there a reason for it?

Thanks!

Author: mole99
Content: FYI your design needs to pass this precheck: https://github.com/wafer-space/gf180mcu-precheck
